text: Khichdi Returns is an Indian television series. Which premiered on 14 April 2018 and airs Star Plus and features the same cast in the series. The series was first launched in 2002, and aired two seasons. The series tentatively titled Khichdi Returns. ==Cast== * Supriya Pathak as Hansa Parekh * Anang Desai as Tulsidas Parekh (Bapuji) * Rajeev Mehra as Praful Parekh * Vandana Pathak as Jayashree Parekh * JD Majethia as Himanshu Seth ==References== Category:2018 Indian television series debuts Category:Hindi-language television series
title: Khichdi (TV series)
